WEBVTT

01:35.700 --> 01:39.980
[Veil of Shadows]

01:39.980 --> 01:42.980
[Episode 8]

01:45.000 --> 01:45.540
Ji Ling!

01:47.950 --> 01:48.380
Hide!

01:53.280 --> 01:54.130
Where are the prayer beads?

01:54.950 --> 01:56.180
I've moved them to a place

01:56.950 --> 01:57.740
where you'll never,

01:57.790 --> 01:59.130
ever find them.

02:03.150 --> 02:04.410
Tie them up with the Demon-Binding Rope!

02:04.920 --> 02:05.570
- Yes, sir. - Yes, sir.

02:54.500 --> 02:56.420
♪Sands in the snow♪

02:56.940 --> 03:00.780
♪Stain whose flawless white?♪

03:01.140 --> 03:03.060
♪A scar in the heart♪

03:03.580 --> 03:07.420
♪A night-blooming flower in moonlight♪

03:08.180 --> 03:14.820
♪Don't pick it, keeping her fleeting grace♪

03:15.340 --> 03:20.740
♪At break of dawn, someone will remember her♪

05:27.580 --> 05:30.340
- Bravo! - Bravo!

05:57.920 --> 05:58.660
Let me do it.

06:30.130 --> 06:31.850
- Bravo! - Bravo!

06:35.740 --> 06:36.380
Bravo!

08:15.190 --> 08:15.980
Had a bad dream?

08:17.190 --> 08:17.810
No.

08:18.800 --> 08:20.020
I was just recalling

08:20.390 --> 08:21.700
a lot of the past.

08:23.160 --> 08:23.930
So long ago,

08:24.720 --> 08:25.780
feels like a past life.

08:26.680 --> 08:27.220
Yeah.

08:28.720 --> 08:29.780
Over a thousand years.

08:31.190 --> 08:33.340
That's many ordinary lifetimes.

08:36.510 --> 08:37.060
Wangyan,

08:38.630 --> 08:39.370
do we really

08:40.440 --> 08:41.890
have to kill Ji Ling?

08:46.390 --> 08:47.300
Didn't you say

08:48.080 --> 08:49.460
Ji Ling isn't the Dragon Deity?

09:28.550 --> 09:29.770
You haven't changed.

09:30.390 --> 09:31.460
Every time you can't sleep,

09:31.510 --> 09:32.820
you come to my place.

09:36.320 --> 09:36.820
Hui.
[*Hui, the same person as Wuyi]

09:37.480 --> 09:39.300
You've never failed a mission.

09:40.360 --> 09:41.530
This is your reward.

09:48.870 --> 09:49.980
Thank you, Master.

09:52.360 --> 09:53.300
I already have

09:53.300 --> 09:54.800
so many colorful stones.

09:55.270 --> 09:56.860
The other sisters don't have any!

10:03.550 --> 10:04.300
What's wrong?

10:05.440 --> 10:06.180
Master,

10:07.360 --> 10:08.220
has the Dragon Deity

10:10.440 --> 10:12.250
truly been corrupted by evil thoughts?

10:15.480 --> 10:16.650
Nothing in this world

10:17.600 --> 10:19.010
is purely good or evil.

10:20.080 --> 10:22.490
Be it human, demon,

10:23.390 --> 10:24.220
deity,

10:25.080 --> 10:25.890
or even devil,

10:26.790 --> 10:28.340
all have a hidden side.

10:30.080 --> 10:31.060
The brighter the light,

10:31.840 --> 10:33.220
the darker the shadow it casts.

10:34.790 --> 10:36.060
Demons can wear painted skin,

10:36.630 --> 10:37.650
humans can wear masks.

10:38.670 --> 10:41.100
Even deities have their obsessions.

10:43.900 --> 10:46.460
♪The great tree softly hums...♪

10:50.910 --> 10:51.580
Wangyan.

10:51.780 --> 10:54.580
♪The grass stands on tiptoes♪

10:54.820 --> 11:00.220
♪The sky's too high and far, afraid it won't hear♪

11:00.660 --> 11:02.820
♪You always said this world...♪

11:02.820 --> 11:05.100
[By Wangyue]
[*Wangyue, the same person as Wangyan]

11:05.100 --> 11:08.060
♪Longing to see it all♪

11:08.740 --> 11:10.020
♪But I only wish♪

11:10.580 --> 11:14.860
♪To stay with you through the coming winter...♪

11:18.080 --> 11:19.220
Over a hundred years,

11:20.240 --> 11:21.580
I've done many things with you

11:21.600 --> 11:23.130
that we had no choice in.

11:23.960 --> 11:25.340
Though we meant to stay pure,

11:26.390 --> 11:27.890
our hands are stained with blood,

11:28.840 --> 11:30.180
and our hearts are full of guilt.

11:32.820 --> 11:35.980
♪Our story♪

11:36.580 --> 11:40.220
♪Is woven with fate, like tangled roots♪

11:40.780 --> 11:47.500
♪Grass and trees stay silent, wearing mist and dew♪

11:48.940 --> 11:52.340
♪Great tree, O great tree♪

11:52.860 --> 11:56.340
♪You brave the wind and bear the rain...♪

11:59.360 --> 12:00.010
Wangyan,

12:00.690 --> 12:01.370
let's go.

12:06.630 --> 12:07.300
Wangyan,

12:08.270 --> 12:08.870
let's go.

12:08.900 --> 12:12.380
♪Time slips by, a swift steed in flight♪

12:12.900 --> 12:18.900
♪But here we root and start to grow♪

12:18.910 --> 12:20.370
This mission is dangerous.

12:21.030 --> 12:22.060
I know

12:22.520 --> 12:24.370
you've developed feelings for Ji Ling.

12:25.470 --> 12:27.320
Whether he is the Dragon Deity or not,

12:27.910 --> 12:29.220
it's a hard choice for you.

12:31.000 --> 12:32.240
I don't want to see you

12:32.670 --> 12:34.850
torn between duty to the world

12:35.600 --> 12:38.010
and drawing blood against your beloved.

12:39.270 --> 12:40.530
Take care of yourself.

12:40.790 --> 12:41.820
I'll be back.

13:14.750 --> 13:16.370
I've been waiting for you.

13:17.600 --> 13:19.340
The Oracle Stone has a new prophecy.

13:20.120 --> 13:21.130
It says...

13:24.200 --> 13:25.580
the Dragon Deity will fall.

13:28.750 --> 13:29.460
I'm not

13:30.960 --> 13:32.130
that easy to kill.

13:33.720 --> 13:34.530
"Won't die"

13:36.000 --> 13:37.130
and "not easy to kill"

13:38.030 --> 13:38.940
are two different things.

13:41.550 --> 13:42.580
What are you trying to say?

13:44.150 --> 13:45.620
You wanted to take back

13:45.620 --> 13:46.510
your power from Xiaowei,

13:47.510 --> 13:49.300
so you sent Li Jie to the Wei mansion.

13:50.480 --> 13:51.340
But you wouldn't risk your life,

13:52.120 --> 13:53.730
so you sent a puppet instead,

13:54.150 --> 13:55.180
Ji Ling,

13:55.910 --> 13:57.940
to go with Li Jie in your place.

13:58.600 --> 13:59.180
Right?

14:02.080 --> 14:03.820
When I saw Ji Ling at the Wei mansion,

14:04.550 --> 14:05.460
I was surprised.

14:06.240 --> 14:08.610
I thought you were just pretending

14:08.670 --> 14:10.340
to be some innocent, lively young man,

14:10.870 --> 14:12.180
acting like you didn't know me.

14:13.630 --> 14:15.580
You're the hunter commander of the Shilin Sect.

14:16.240 --> 14:17.060
And you?

14:17.870 --> 14:19.060
What exactly are you?

14:21.440 --> 14:22.130
Me?

14:24.790 --> 14:26.530
Just an ordinary hunter, no flower on my forehead.

14:27.440 --> 14:28.100
What's wrong?

14:28.840 --> 14:30.100
Were you joking,

14:30.630 --> 14:31.530
or were you serious?

14:32.600 --> 14:35.100
Not until Xiaowei gravely wounded Ji Ling,

14:40.670 --> 14:43.300
and the wound's edge showed wood chips.

14:45.150 --> 14:46.650
I figured Ji Ling and Li Jie

14:46.720 --> 14:48.610
might run into a Formless Moon member there.

14:49.880 --> 14:51.770
I just didn't expect it to be you,

14:52.270 --> 14:53.100
of all people.

14:55.270 --> 14:56.650
When things are too coincidental,

14:58.150 --> 14:59.850
someone's usually pulling the strings.

15:00.960 --> 15:03.460
The Fox Queen specifically sent Wuyi and me.

15:03.750 --> 15:05.460
She knows about Ji Ling.

15:06.480 --> 15:07.250
She said

15:07.750 --> 15:10.610
Ji Ling and Wuyi are fated ones.

15:11.320 --> 15:12.250
What does that mean?

15:13.720 --> 15:15.060
Fated ones?

15:17.080 --> 15:18.010
Now, your power

15:18.010 --> 15:19.580
has passed to Wu Shiguang.

15:20.120 --> 15:21.410
Only one piece, for now,

15:21.630 --> 15:23.300
not enough to seal your fate.

15:24.600 --> 15:26.340
But the Oracle Stone never errs.

15:28.480 --> 15:29.580
The Dragon Deity's fall

15:30.240 --> 15:31.250
will come, sooner or later.

15:32.670 --> 15:34.530
That's why I need your help.

15:36.510 --> 15:37.490
What do you want me to do?

15:38.270 --> 15:39.660
Get close to Wu Shiguang.

15:40.600 --> 15:42.180
Find a way to take the prayer beads

15:43.270 --> 15:44.250
and bring them to me.

15:46.200 --> 15:47.220
Those beads know their owner.

15:48.270 --> 15:49.130
Taking them

15:50.150 --> 15:51.100
won't be easy.

15:54.750 --> 15:55.980
Foxes from the Formless Moon

15:56.720 --> 15:58.130
are masters at seduction.

15:59.080 --> 16:00.180
A mere Wu Shiguang

16:00.870 --> 16:01.850
shouldn't be too hard

16:03.000 --> 16:03.580
for you.

16:07.120 --> 16:07.890
Right.

16:11.630 --> 16:12.770
For a thousand years,

16:13.440 --> 16:15.130
I've played countless roles,

16:16.440 --> 16:17.980
had countless family,

16:19.150 --> 16:19.940
lovers,

16:21.840 --> 16:22.580
and dearest friends.

16:24.870 --> 16:26.130
But truth and lies blur,

16:27.200 --> 16:28.100
this life is but a dream.

16:29.510 --> 16:30.650
I can barely remember

16:30.670 --> 16:31.530
who I am anymore.

16:34.000 --> 16:34.730
You're tired?

16:45.030 --> 16:45.610
What about you?

16:48.320 --> 16:49.220
Wearing a skin

16:50.270 --> 16:51.340
for too long,

16:53.030 --> 16:55.490
you'll forget the heart beneath.

16:57.840 --> 16:58.650
But the heart

17:00.390 --> 17:02.530
always remembers who it truly is.

17:04.020 --> 17:07.180
♪I raise my face, and snow veils my eyes♪

17:07.260 --> 17:10.060
♪Yet a glimmer shines through♪

17:10.540 --> 17:13.900
♪Spring mud endures the winter and buries petals♪

17:14.050 --> 17:17.700
♪Who sings this song of longing?♪

17:17.710 --> 17:19.060
I hope this is the last time.

17:19.380 --> 17:20.820
♪Everything breaks apart...♪

17:21.070 --> 17:21.890
Trust me,

17:23.750 --> 17:25.120
this is the last time.

17:25.140 --> 17:25.940
♪It's just a dream...♪

17:26.360 --> 17:27.050
After this,

17:28.280 --> 17:30.170
you and everyone in the Formless Moon

17:31.680 --> 17:32.730
will be truly free.

17:32.730 --> 17:39.900
♪Ah, if it hurts, grow a flower♪

17:42.920 --> 17:43.570
Wu Shiguang,

17:44.160 --> 17:45.140
do something!

17:45.510 --> 17:46.180
Wu Shiguang?

17:46.550 --> 17:47.220
Wu Shiguang?

18:01.070 --> 18:01.860
I rubbed it off!

18:02.550 --> 18:03.220
I rubbed the rope loose!

18:04.310 --> 18:05.090
My spell did that.

18:07.880 --> 18:08.220
Why...

18:08.480 --> 18:10.300
why didn't you use that sooner?

18:10.440 --> 18:11.690
My bones are stiff!

18:11.810 --> 18:12.810
You're a weasel.

18:13.400 --> 18:14.860
Your bones are the softest in the world.

18:15.160 --> 18:15.940
Stop playing the victim.

18:16.440 --> 18:18.050
You just make up rumors out of thin air!

18:21.440 --> 18:22.460
What now?

19:07.720 --> 19:08.330
Indeed,

19:09.310 --> 19:10.860
a weasel's fart really does work best.

19:11.510 --> 19:12.530
Can you stop with the rumors?

19:15.270 --> 19:17.460
That's black smoke from my blade, alright?

19:19.830 --> 19:20.330
So?

19:21.000 --> 19:21.620
Praise me!

19:36.680 --> 19:37.860
Be careful!

19:38.400 --> 19:39.940
I don't want to vanish into thin air.

19:42.640 --> 19:43.010
What are you doing?

19:43.680 --> 19:44.250
I'm here.

20:00.780 --> 20:01.420
Commander Li,

20:01.880 --> 20:02.700
as you instructed,

20:02.830 --> 20:03.770
I let them escape.

20:04.440 --> 20:05.330
What now?

20:06.920 --> 20:07.570
Follow them.

20:08.720 --> 20:10.010
He'll definitely go get the prayer beads.

21:33.790 --> 21:35.140
Didn't you go back to the Formless Moon?

21:36.270 --> 21:37.420
The moment we parted,

21:37.830 --> 21:39.090
I couldn't sleep.

21:39.830 --> 21:40.860
I told myself

21:41.200 --> 21:42.010
I shouldn't think of you,

21:43.070 --> 21:43.940
and I can't think of you.

21:45.160 --> 21:45.900
But,

21:46.640 --> 21:47.940
when feelings arise,

21:48.590 --> 21:50.020
the heart follows.

21:51.070 --> 21:52.540
So I had to come find you.

21:54.000 --> 21:55.730
Formless Moon foxes are truly something.

21:57.000 --> 21:58.140
You make tracking someone

21:58.920 --> 22:00.290
sound so seductive.

22:00.720 --> 22:01.620
Seductive?

22:18.960 --> 22:20.090
You've misunderstood me, sir.

22:21.550 --> 22:23.180
The one tracking you isn't me.

22:24.480 --> 22:25.460
It's Li Jie.

22:55.720 --> 22:56.490
He meant to let us go.

22:58.030 --> 22:59.940
Ye Changsheng doesn't need a token on him.

23:02.680 --> 23:03.530
Exactly.

23:04.790 --> 23:06.890
I trapped him in my maze formation,

23:07.440 --> 23:08.250
or else

23:09.200 --> 23:10.940
Li Jie would've caught you by now.

23:34.510 --> 23:35.730
Instead of thanking me,

23:37.880 --> 23:39.050
you nearly

23:39.920 --> 23:40.770
deflowered me.

23:41.830 --> 23:42.940
Nearly destroyed you.

23:43.790 --> 23:44.570
Don't talk nonsense,

23:45.350 --> 23:46.860
and that's what your name implies.

23:50.070 --> 23:51.090
So why are you here?

23:51.680 --> 23:52.530
To help you.

23:54.720 --> 23:55.730
I'm used to going solo.

23:56.510 --> 23:57.530
I don't need your help.

23:58.680 --> 23:59.700
Killing the Dragon Deity

24:00.920 --> 24:02.620
is no easy task.

24:05.200 --> 24:06.730
You sure you don't need help?

24:08.830 --> 24:09.770
I'm killing him

24:10.960 --> 24:12.570
to avenge my entire clan.

24:14.640 --> 24:15.140
What about you?

24:18.480 --> 24:20.140
The Oracle Stone gave a prophecy.

24:21.880 --> 24:23.050
I have no choice.

24:26.680 --> 24:27.980
You're a cunning fox,

24:29.070 --> 24:30.330
always deceiving and running off.

24:31.920 --> 24:32.810
Why should I trust you?

24:33.720 --> 24:35.530
Have I ever deceived you?

24:36.720 --> 24:37.330
Back at the Wei mansion,

24:38.240 --> 24:39.700
who claimed to be after Xiaowei

24:40.720 --> 24:42.050
but ended up wounded by me?

24:45.200 --> 24:46.660
That was to help you.

24:48.310 --> 24:49.770
Lu Wuyi's not easy to fool.

24:49.860 --> 24:50.700
Wangyan,

24:51.000 --> 24:51.660
are you okay?

24:52.310 --> 24:53.620
You wanted to buy time

24:53.680 --> 24:55.140
for those Shilin Sect hunters.

24:55.680 --> 24:57.420
So I pretended you wounded me,

24:57.720 --> 24:58.570
to hold my sister back.

25:03.310 --> 25:04.900
That hit of yours was pretty hard.

25:06.510 --> 25:08.050
And now you blame me?

25:09.350 --> 25:10.730
You even deceive your own sister.

25:12.510 --> 25:14.090
I didn't want to deceive her either.

25:14.920 --> 25:16.510
But that move isn't just for Xiaowei,

25:17.350 --> 25:18.520
it's for you.

25:21.920 --> 25:23.180
You're in my heart.

25:25.880 --> 25:27.150
And I know

25:27.270 --> 25:29.110
you have feelings for me too.

25:41.310 --> 25:42.900
Your heart's racing.

25:47.750 --> 25:48.620
Want to work together?

25:49.510 --> 25:50.380
Show your cards.

25:52.270 --> 25:53.050
What do you have?

25:56.750 --> 25:57.950
That depends

26:00.550 --> 26:01.460
on what you want.

26:03.440 --> 26:04.330
I want to know

26:05.590 --> 26:06.940
where the next piece of Dragon Deity's Power is.

26:39.270 --> 26:40.860
I've been dreading telling you this,

26:41.880 --> 26:43.090
but Wangyue has also turned.

26:45.310 --> 26:47.220
I know you two are like sisters.

26:48.110 --> 26:48.770
So,

26:49.200 --> 26:50.330
go find her,

26:51.110 --> 26:52.140
uncover the truth,

26:53.400 --> 26:54.290
or perhaps

26:54.960 --> 26:56.530
help her find her way back.

26:57.310 --> 26:58.140
Master,

26:58.960 --> 27:00.180
I will find out the truth,

27:01.160 --> 27:02.900
and prove she hasn't betrayed us.

27:05.240 --> 27:05.940
Wangyan.

27:34.400 --> 27:36.380
You blame me for liking Ji Ling.

27:37.790 --> 27:39.090
But you're into someone too.

27:41.070 --> 27:42.530
Helping him gather the Dragon Deity's Power

27:43.070 --> 27:44.180
was a mission from our master.

27:47.160 --> 27:47.730
Really?

27:49.550 --> 27:50.090
Of course.

27:56.590 --> 27:58.050
Ji Ling is innocent and kind.

27:59.400 --> 28:00.490
I do like him.

28:02.590 --> 28:04.140
But right now, the greater good comes first.

28:04.680 --> 28:05.660
I understand that.

28:06.640 --> 28:07.380
Besides,

28:07.920 --> 28:09.090
he's not the Dragon Deity.

28:10.310 --> 28:11.900
It's the Dragon Deity turning evil,

28:12.310 --> 28:13.530
destined to fall.

28:14.920 --> 28:16.700
Ji Ling was just deceived.

28:18.350 --> 28:19.380
He'll understand me.

28:25.880 --> 28:26.490
Wangyan,

28:27.350 --> 28:28.730
don't leave me behind again.

28:31.110 --> 28:31.790
I won't.

28:33.440 --> 28:34.960
No matter where,

28:35.960 --> 28:37.050
we'll be together.

28:50.750 --> 28:51.420
Wangyan,

28:52.310 --> 28:53.620
why are you

28:54.030 --> 28:55.620
so fragrant today?

28:58.000 --> 28:58.700
Do I?

29:01.070 --> 29:02.090
Maybe just the grass

29:02.830 --> 29:03.980
damp with night dew.

30:21.140 --> 30:23.340
♪Moonlight falters♪

30:23.940 --> 30:26.460
♪Spreading in silence♪

30:27.900 --> 30:31.380
♪Candles burn through our farewells♪

30:33.780 --> 30:35.980
♪Trapped in this body♪

30:36.660 --> 30:39.500
♪This borrowed halo♪

30:40.380 --> 30:44.460
♪Tears unshed, pain untold♪

30:49.660 --> 30:52.140
♪How pitiful, how sad♪

30:56.020 --> 30:59.620
♪Too scared to accept♪

31:01.700 --> 31:04.780
♪Just lend me one more tomorrow♪

31:05.100 --> 31:07.940
♪To go back and see my hometown♪

31:08.300 --> 31:11.100
♪Holding all my bitter regrets♪

31:11.260 --> 31:13.980
♪As I drift farther away♪

31:14.500 --> 31:17.420
♪I won't wipe my tears dry...♪

31:17.430 --> 31:18.410
I'm real.

31:24.300 --> 31:26.740
♪No more longing♪

31:51.350 --> 31:52.940
I don't understand love,

31:53.240 --> 31:54.330
nor hate.

31:55.030 --> 31:56.700
I don't think I've ever loved anyone,

31:57.240 --> 31:59.140
or hated anyone either.

32:00.960 --> 32:01.810
I guess

32:02.310 --> 32:03.220
I'm just...

32:03.400 --> 32:03.980
a woodenhead.

32:07.510 --> 32:08.220
Fine,

32:09.000 --> 32:10.380
I'm a woodenhead then.

32:12.400 --> 32:13.220
No, you're not.

32:38.830 --> 32:39.770
Master Dragon Deity.

32:43.110 --> 32:43.530
I...

32:47.160 --> 32:47.660
I...

32:58.200 --> 32:59.140
Master Chi Wen.

33:00.880 --> 33:01.570
Wu Shiguang said

33:03.480 --> 33:04.900
I'm a puppet.

33:06.880 --> 33:08.770
But I'm clearly a fox

33:08.770 --> 33:09.660
from South Mountain.

33:10.720 --> 33:12.140
There must be some mistake,

33:13.750 --> 33:14.380
right?

33:17.030 --> 33:18.140
So you found out.

33:20.590 --> 33:21.430
You are indeed

33:21.430 --> 33:22.770
a puppet I made.

33:24.640 --> 33:25.660
Not a fox.

33:27.070 --> 33:28.010
No... no way.

33:30.160 --> 33:30.980
It's not true.

33:32.110 --> 33:33.380
I was born on South Mountain,

33:33.380 --> 33:35.290
in a cave by Yumian Lake.

33:36.080 --> 33:37.770
I was a blind fox.

33:38.670 --> 33:39.540
Outside the cave,

33:40.480 --> 33:41.970
there were lots of raspberries

33:43.190 --> 33:44.100
and wood sorrel.

33:45.200 --> 33:45.860
Then,

33:46.230 --> 33:48.050
I was hit by falling rocks,

33:48.640 --> 33:49.570
and was about to die.

33:49.880 --> 33:50.860
You saved me,

33:51.070 --> 33:52.500
and healed my eyes.

33:53.160 --> 33:54.300
You even gave me power,

33:54.560 --> 33:55.500
and sent me to save people.

33:56.950 --> 33:57.980
I remember all of this.

33:58.750 --> 33:59.820
How could I possibly be...

34:01.110 --> 34:02.250
a puppet?

34:03.310 --> 34:04.770
If I can give you power,

34:07.590 --> 34:09.140
I can also give you memories.

34:11.480 --> 34:12.130
Give me...

34:15.760 --> 34:16.490
memories?

34:23.320 --> 34:24.090
So,

34:28.710 --> 34:30.130
all of it is fake?

34:32.280 --> 34:33.300
You made it all up?

34:35.590 --> 34:36.260
In this world,

34:36.800 --> 34:37.940
there never was a blind fox

34:38.110 --> 34:39.300
like me?

34:42.030 --> 34:42.940
No Ji Ling?

34:46.550 --> 34:47.170
Is that true?

34:53.440 --> 34:54.300
Master...

34:56.190 --> 34:57.650
why did you create

34:57.650 --> 34:58.570
someone like me...

35:02.320 --> 35:03.260
a puppet?

35:06.000 --> 35:07.340
Are you blaming me?

35:11.590 --> 35:13.130
I granted you life

35:14.510 --> 35:16.380
to experience the human world.

35:17.920 --> 35:19.260
Isn't that a gift?

35:20.630 --> 35:22.420
Being a puppet, controlled,

35:24.880 --> 35:26.010
deceived by my most trusted,

35:26.920 --> 35:28.340
my dearest one...

35:29.800 --> 35:30.780
you call that a gift?

35:30.840 --> 35:31.860
Don't be insolent.

35:34.630 --> 35:35.490
Master,

35:36.840 --> 35:38.090
did you create me

35:39.710 --> 35:40.820
just to have a puppet

35:40.880 --> 35:42.530
you could manipulate at will?

35:44.000 --> 35:45.820
Or did you need someone

35:46.760 --> 35:48.300
who could die in your place anytime?

35:52.840 --> 35:53.610
Does it matter?

35:54.110 --> 35:54.780
Yes, it matters!

35:56.400 --> 35:57.460
To me,

35:58.400 --> 35:59.340
it matters a lot!

36:02.510 --> 36:03.900
Even if I'm a puppet,

36:05.190 --> 36:05.940
I want to know

36:05.960 --> 36:07.010
why I exist!

36:08.550 --> 36:09.860
Even as a puppet,

36:11.360 --> 36:13.460
if I can protect you,

36:14.440 --> 36:16.170
then my existence has meaning!

36:17.550 --> 36:19.090
Then I'm not just a piece of wood!

36:21.070 --> 36:23.210
I'm my own unique self!

36:25.510 --> 36:27.050
I am Ji Ling!

36:30.630 --> 36:32.380
I am Ji Ling...

36:39.510 --> 36:39.980
I...

36:40.440 --> 36:42.010
I am Ji Ling...

36:42.980 --> 36:49.100
♪Snowflakes gently hold me close♪

36:49.460 --> 36:53.980
♪Like a drifting boat finds its final shore...♪

37:00.070 --> 37:00.900
Follow me.

37:03.460 --> 37:08.620
♪Asking the night why it keeps me bound♪

37:10.780 --> 37:17.780
♪Has anyone heard my call?♪

37:18.020 --> 37:23.100
♪Like a feather waiting for its final fall♪

37:33.840 --> 37:35.300
How will I find you?

37:37.360 --> 37:37.980
Don't worry.

37:38.960 --> 37:39.820
I will find you.

38:16.960 --> 38:19.860
Still think you're unique?

38:35.480 --> 38:36.610
I always hoped

38:37.510 --> 38:39.350
you could stay innocent forever,

38:40.110 --> 38:41.380
living a carefree life.

38:43.030 --> 38:44.610
You're the piece of my youth, my past,

38:45.960 --> 38:47.490
that I most wanted to keep.

38:49.800 --> 38:50.570
What a pity.

40:55.660 --> 40:56.820
♪It's your light♪

40:57.020 --> 40:58.900
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

40:59.060 --> 41:02.180
♪That set the night alight♪

41:02.540 --> 41:09.060
♪And lead me through the fight♪

41:10.820 --> 41:12.700
♪Jade in the lake, sand in my hand♪

41:13.140 --> 41:17.580
♪Let bitter seeds grow, let fate bloom♪

41:18.380 --> 41:20.060
♪Face in the mirror, veiled in mist♪

41:20.220 --> 41:25.620
♪Till snow has kissed dark hair to white♪

41:26.380 --> 41:31.780
♪Night lamp burning by the old table♪

41:34.100 --> 41:40.140
♪Stitch by stitch, mending moonlight♪

41:41.100 --> 41:43.260
♪The dancing light, the shattered wave♪

41:43.540 --> 41:48.380
♪Are all my helpless, drifting haze♪

41:48.740 --> 41:51.060
♪The boiling frost, the stubborn stare♪

41:51.260 --> 41:56.340
♪Are all the pride I'll never wear♪

41:56.580 --> 41:58.580
♪Your shoulder, your tear-bright eyes♪

41:58.860 --> 42:03.220
♪Are the strength that lifts my dreams to the skies♪

42:04.220 --> 42:11.180
♪Stay with me, let's gaze above♪

42:27.740 --> 42:30.700
♪Nowhere to rest, nowhere to hide♪

42:31.780 --> 42:35.180
♪Bare in body yet boundless inside♪

42:35.980 --> 42:38.500
♪Nothing to seek, nothing to erase♪

42:38.740 --> 42:41.820
♪Like water gone, like the formless moon♪

42:42.220 --> 42:44.540
♪Let every dream and wild desire♪

42:45.060 --> 42:49.460
♪Forge the edge that lifts us higher♪

42:49.700 --> 42:51.860
♪Bells through endless time, sun and moon alike in shine♪

42:52.260 --> 42:57.220
♪Love and hate all earn their crown♪

42:57.460 --> 42:58.620
♪It's your light♪

42:58.820 --> 43:00.660
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

43:00.860 --> 43:03.980
♪That set the night alight♪

43:04.740 --> 43:14.180
♪And lead me sailing afar♪
